        "creation_date": 1418975545,
        "body": "<p>When you you use emit(), the first parameter represent the key of your index.\nif you call the view using startKey and endKey, then these two values should match the indexed key (same order). <\/p>\n\n<p>for example<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>[doc.links[linkedTo], doc.Date.value ]\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>is you index key so your startKey and endKey should always use the same format (linkedTo first followed by date).<\/p>\n\n<p>Also if you use descending order param for your query, do not forget to invert startKey and endKey.<\/p>\n",
